Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說千影今天一整天都在打掃地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被叫去打掃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵…敵襲?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箭書?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也稍微考慮一下射入的位置啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  是命給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟有什麼事情  看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽一直吵著讓我們要和行人相親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和宮內姐都沒什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說為何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有凜姐了  呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和行人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:01:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍姐會過去  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火速回來  是命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:50.00,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決勝負吧  忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命是忍者的末裔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影流忍者一族
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長女叫宮內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次女叫忍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三女就是命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忍者三姐妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  是人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有牛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  是忍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忍者三姐妹中的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍怎麼了  生病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶她去老奶奶那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚…肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強的食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子那麼餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這幾天都沒好好吃過一餐飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  牛排
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想進行一夜的修行卻迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到的時候已經過了好幾個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幾個月…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍是島上第一的方向癡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真難得還是回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  妹妹命燃起狼煙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過的面孔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍在行人漂流到島之前就已經開始劍的修行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  漂流到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  漂流到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必和在下…在下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是命信中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用劍來比試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比試?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來不是相親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  行人殿下一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…從剛才開始就聽不懂在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的劍術水平已經如雷鳴暴風一樣聞名各森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷鳴暴風?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在撒播謠言…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在修行途中的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵  又是我贏了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你也強了許多喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後修行的旅途也加油喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…請讓在下再在島虎大人身邊接受修行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道不久前漂流到島上的少年的事情喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:05:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這島上有少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…在下這段時間沒有回過村子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話去見一見那少年就好了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他擁有打倒北部主人的本領
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是島上唯一的劍客喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那北部的主人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那少年的名為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你不會錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是我…不過說是劍客就太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他的證言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個的話我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北部主人被打得軟弱無力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事情是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能給我如此的一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人  太強勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他還有像是用木刀把岩石切開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是用駭人的劍術把樹刻成百個木雕熊人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也聽說能讓瀑布逆流這類事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺被傳得太假了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人都會感到奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下  我希望與你進行劍術的切磋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快…快…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們也去吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是和以前一樣笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是忍者啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是忍者而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在以劍的道路為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍要住下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是除非行人接受決勝負不然不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說些什麼讓她回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也反對打架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是忍很頑固的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要與我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要與我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要與我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要與我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要與我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要與我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要與我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:10.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要與我決勝負…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍…忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  小鈴殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  打算一直跟著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  武士不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  行人  是條大魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我更強的人在島上到處都有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別謙虛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是在下武士的直覺告訴我  你並非平凡之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  這不是大魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請與我決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不打了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真纏人啊  忍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經快輸給她了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為男人的我對女生揮劍是違反我的原則的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼男人對女人揮劍就會違反行人殿下的原則
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的家訓是男人要保護女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將劍朝向該保護的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是本末倒置了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近小鈴都沒有偷偷進來了  完全大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  泡過頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:10:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你擦背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了好幾遍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你答應和我決勝負之前不會離開你身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟這個意思不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  你就乖乖地讓我來幫你擦背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然捨身保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一決勝負  就能不再糾纏行人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和忍一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天明明還反對的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了嗎  快一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對行人做了不好的事情了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多…謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和北部主人戰鬥後實力確實提升了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想和忍決勝負嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  和女孩決勝負什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不清楚  但是小鈴忽然擺出令人害怕的表情說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我去一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這是便當和傷藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點結束和忍的決鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你還真遲鈍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個…既然接受了決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在意對手而放水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是違反禮儀的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我是想堂堂正正決鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果放水的話到時受傷的也許是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍…忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來不是要決鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼  不是理所當然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那衣服是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在來這裡迷路了被千影救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說決勝負什麼的還以為是約會什麼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝者是先擊打到對方一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是一方認輸就算贏  這樣可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒開始決鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要觀戰的話就給我安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始堂堂正正地比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽說過了 行人大人居然那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  忍也好快完全看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:15:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和預想一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干炸  這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和行人說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果放水的話到時受傷的也許是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能說你會輸  不過你不可能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請關注兩人的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍的攻擊只是亂揮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過動作太快  我的攻擊完全打不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下  雖然動作不是很快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的攻擊卻全被看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說兩人都無法擊中對方一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以無法決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是高水平對決了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那如何做行人才能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作如果能超出對方預想的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作超出對方預想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干炸所說的就是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那招就不能贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心  你和傳說那樣的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  忍的身體能力也好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用必殺技決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺技
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…又不是漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:28.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍認真起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是承認公子的實力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出現了  忍法金縛術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是  是忍法影操縱術才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  這是忍法人類聚集之術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我先上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多方陣影分身太刀之術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了  忍的終極忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有七個忍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超出對方的預想的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決出勝負了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  一直看著忍的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按到並抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加超越了對方預想的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對的  本來想救忍的碰巧就用手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這手…是這手不好…這手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你究竟做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在下輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是什麼法術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部被抓住的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身被不知名的衝擊擊中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使不上力而無法站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是  那不是法術什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是說先擊打到對方一次就勝利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是觸碰對方身體行人的勝利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:20:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…剛才是事故
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負還未…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是閣下的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊中一次就是一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因你的招術使不上力無法站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  勝者是行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍  請萬事小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.18,0:22:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(540,80)}{\fad(800,800)\fs20\bord3\4a&HFF}\N\N\N\N{\1c&HC43A2C\3c&HFFFFFF}次回　　　　　　　　　　　{\fs10}\N\N{\fs20}「去揭秘吧  偵探（前篇）」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚睡得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很累  睡得很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍安全地踏上修行的旅程了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.75,0:22:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大碗  再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍…為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.83,0:23:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修行怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  其實是想出鑽研出更好的劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.38,0:23:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  行人殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收在下為您劍術的弟子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.23,0:23:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟…弟子?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請來這裡教導我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.99,0:23:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度好快  而且好近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不會再迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅  請多多指教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:23.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴的家
